  "instructions": [
    "preheat oven to 375 degrees fahrenheit.",
    "mix buckwheat groats, olive oil, and red wine vinegar in a bowl.",
    "add grated carrot and zucchini, and mix well.",
    "transfer mixture to a molcajete and smooth the top.",
    "bake for 25 minutes, or until the buckwheat is lightly toasted.",
    "remove from oven and top with sour cream mixture.",
